{"id":24838957851,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAFyIRrGw","head_branch":"fix_missing_name_oauth2_authorization","head_sha":"017c599e0904c7abc8173f514d478f0c76cf931c","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":52862,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: harden OAuth2 authorization + consent runtime state","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":65887258296,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAPVy_GuA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851","pull_requests":[{"id":3560227302,"number":23675,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/23675","head":{"ref":"fix_missing_name_oauth2_authorization","sha":"e5bce0e2c0e1367a1e64ad4e598a43305f475d03","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"fa64caf8fbafb328e86a139bdbad3de8caf3d720","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-04-23T13:48:03Z","updated_at":"2026-04-23T14:03:59Z","run_started_at":"2026-04-23T13:48:03Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/65887258296","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24838957851/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix(sec): reject /api/metadata DELETE of OAuth2 authorization + consent\n\nThe ObjectBundleHook added earlier only overrides validate(), which\nValidationHooksCheck dispatches on CREATE / UPDATE / CREATE_AND_UPDATE.\nServiceConfig.validatorsByImportStrategy() registers only\n[SecurityCheck, DeletionCheck] for ImportStrategy.DELETE — so a\nsuperuser calling POST /api/metadata?importStrategy=DELETE with\nenumerated Dhis2OAuth2Authorization / Dhis2OAuth2AuthorizationConsent\nUIDs would wipe every access/refresh token, authorization code, device\ncode and consent grant in one call, invalidating every live OAuth\nsession. The hook's own javadoc claim of \"closes the metadata-import\nwrite path\" was therefore only true for CREATE/UPDATE.\n\nAdds OAuth2RuntimeStateCheck — a dedicated ObjectValidationCheck that\nemits E6023 and marks the object for removal whenever the bundle\ntargets one of these two classes. Registered at the head of the DELETE\nchain so it fires before DeletionCheck / session.delete. OAuth2Meta\ndataImportRejectionTest gains two DELETE cases (one per type) that\nseed a row via the store and assert a rejected DELETE leaves the row\nintact.\n\nNormal severity (requires superuser, DoS only — cannot forge bearer\ntokens) but the gap was invisible to CI and contradicted the stated\ncontract.\n\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"},"id":"017c599e0904c7abc8173f514d478f0c76cf931c","tree_id":"3a9c0c0cd9831ecf90d5082ece1a8838fd46ab59","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:47:51Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users